You’re definitely in the right place. I found the deeper issue: the Contacts view timed out on page 3 of the full load, so the app zeroed the Contacts array.

I hotfixed the Supabase view so it gates by CRM access but no longer runs the heavy join under per-row invoker RLS. Verified a browser-style authenticated load now fetches all `8,654` contacts across all pages.

Live site is HTTP 200 and proxy is healthy. Please refresh Contacts once more now.

Committed and pushed the DB migration record too: `647938d fix: gate contact view without invoker RLS`.

::git-commit{cwd="/worksp/popcrm-web"}
::git-push{cwd="/worksp/popcrm-web" branch="main"}

